      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:5:3:115:2",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) اطْلُبُوا الْأَوْلَادَ مِنْ أُمَّهَاتِ الْأَوْلَادِ فَإِنَّ فِي أَرْحَامِهِنَّ الْبَرَكَةَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Humeyd Bin Ziyad, from Ibn Sama’at, from one of his companion, from Abu Hamza, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Ali<sup>asws</sup> Bin Al-Husayn<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said: ‘Seek the children from the mothers, for in their wombs is the Blessing’."
        ]
      }
    },
